061b1766ae","frontmatter":{"name":"designrock","email":null,"friendlyDate":"April 09, 2014","iso8601Date":"2014-04-09T23:30:26.000Z","published":null},"html":"<p>Thanks for recommending the app. Love it.</p>"}},{"node":{"id":"6ebe1994-5c94-5791-944c-9cb7764eb2a4","frontmatter":{"name":"Kevin Bradberry","email":null,"friendlyDate":"August 26, 2014","iso8601Date":"2014-08-26T21:01:12.000Z","published":null},"html":"<p>iPad art fan, here. I love how you’ve mixed free time creativity, generosity,\nand income stream. Very cool. I think I’ll share this article on my blog.</p>"}},{"node":{"id":"4ec5a6ed-01a3-5090-8631-1ce9b445b3b8","frontmatter":{"name":"Michael Rose","email":"1ce71bc10b86565464b612093d89707e","friendlyDate":"August 27, 2014","iso8601Date":"2014-08-27T01:07:54.000Z","published":null},"html":"<p>Thanks Kevin. Appreciate the kind words and potential share on your blog.</p>"}},{"node":{"id":"2e367060-5fdf-55ca-a369-e51c6fa83a2f","frontmatter":{"name":"Kevin Bradberry","email":null,"friendlyDate":"September 03, 2014","iso8601Date":"2014-09-03T11:38:23.000Z","published":null},"html":"<p>Posted it a few days ago. My blog is young, so take this with a grain of salt,\nbut it became my second most popular post\n<a href=\"http://kevinbradberry.net/2014/08/27/ipad-artist-michael-rose/\">http://kevinbradberry.net/2014/08/27/ipad-artist-michael-rose/</a>. The credit is\nall yours.</p>"}}]}},"pageContext":{"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/paperfaces/veganwendy-portrait/","title":"The First PaperFaces Portrait","categories":["paperfaces"],"tags":["portrait","illustration","Paper for iOS","tattoo"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/28041/opensource/github.com/mmistakes/made-mistakes-gatsby/src/posts/paperfaces/veganwendy-portrait.md"},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/notes/romance-egg-engagement/","title":"Easter egg marriage proposal","categories":["notes"],"tags":["life"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/28041/opensource/github.com/mmistakes/made-mistakes-gatsby/src/posts/notes/ro